Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.82,0:01:23.33,CMTS,,0,0,0,,註: "土左衛門"的語源是來自江湖時代享保年間的相撲力士"成瀨川土左衛門"，\N由於他皮膚蒼白又相當胖，身體膨脹的溺水者屍體便被說是"像土左衛門那樣"，\N這個比喻就固定下來成為溺水者屍體的代稱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.83,0:00:05.79,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,請指引我們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.36,0:00:08.63,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天還是敵人今天就要當朋友嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.91,0:00:11.21,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,來給大爺跪一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.21,0:00:14.61,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,做得到嗎 自傲的貴族們
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.66,0:00:22.06,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,現在只能做這些
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.58,0:00:24.98,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,早晚有一天會謝罪的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.64,0:00:29.52,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,少爺和貴族小姐都那麼誇張啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.68,0:00:31.53,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,隨你們的便
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.95,0:00:33.24,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.74,0:00:34.30,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,好乾脆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.45,0:00:37.28,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,交待和道歉都不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.96,0:00:39.62,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我也幹掉了你們的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.85,0:00:40.74,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,彼此彼此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.81,0:00:43.97,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但是指引就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.97,0:00:45.08,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我不適合那個
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.21,0:00:47.85,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道你想知道什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.85,0:00:48.90,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,隨便做就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.41,0:00:52.21,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,只要不礙我的事 我也不會說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.91,0:00:53.63,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,太感謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.19,0:00:55.42,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,說這個還早
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.13,0:01:00.22,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,和我們一起走就意味著能睡覺的夜晚不會再來了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.63,0:01:04.73,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,要出現了伊斯多洛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.97,0:01:06.06,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.12,0:01:07.26,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,法爾納塞小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.26,0:01:09.06,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,請你不要讓火熄滅
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.31,0:01:11.22,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我記住了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.77,0:01:13.28,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以 卡思嘉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.28,0:01:14.53,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,擅自亂走的話
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.27,0:01:17.03,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.82,0:01:23.33,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,來吧 你們這些土左衛門
Comment: 0,0:03:05.63,0:03:06.00,DefaultSub,,0,0,0,,/------START-------/
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.12,0:03:07.39,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,看打
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.39,0:03:08.43,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.80,0:03:11.39,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我摻了些昨天的狐狸的骨髓
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.64,0:03:13.85,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你真是盡職啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.35,0:03:17.11,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你這身材把劍舉過頭頂是要鬧哪出
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.21,0:03:20.11,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你要想靠殺人吃飯就好好動腦想想
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.85,0:03:23.15,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,再加些鹽如何
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.15,0:03:24.86,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,畢竟是運動之後呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.09,0:03:27.20,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,多洛皮 一會兒就要吃飯了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.20,0:03:29.08,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,把法爾醬她們叫來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.21,0:03:31.46,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你們管得越來越多了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.58,0:03:36.84,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,法爾納塞小姐 這是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.95,0:03:39.00,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,蘑菇 剛剛找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.04,0:03:42.17,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這些是毒蘑菇 不能吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.17,0:03:43.84,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.20,0:03:46.14,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 我最好的衣服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.14,0:03:48.18,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,就這樣吧 剩下的我來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.20,0:03:52.27,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.76,0:03:55.06,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,夠了 你把卡思嘉和火看好就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.99,0:04:03.95,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,深刻感到自己什麼也做不呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.77,0:04:06.13,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,讓人笑掉大牙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.30,0:04:09.78,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我對你做了很過分的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.17,0:04:12.00,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我要謝罪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.49,0:04:23.09,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我是如此渺小啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.92,0:04:28.60,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,卡思嘉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.13,0:04:30.59,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微等我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.13,0:04:34.60,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,用這個稍微補充一下食物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.30,0:04:37.31,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 不要跑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.10,0:04:40.32,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.98,0:04:45.45,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,卡思嘉小姐 回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.69,0:04:49.87,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,卡思嘉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.08,0:04:51.87,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,卡思嘉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.49,0:04:57.00,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是我的 是我的責任
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.66,0:05:03.17,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,卡思嘉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.71,0:05:08.76,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦 回去的路也不知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.18,0:05:21.86,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,卡思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.23,0:05:24.19,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,有人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.45,0:05:27.65,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,塞爾彼高
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.48,0:05:33.45,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,有了有了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.74,0:05:34.87,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.20,0:05:40.13,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,法爾納塞小姐 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.60,0:05:42.46,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 你真悠閒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.00,0:05:46.67,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我們可是保護著卡思嘉 大做了一場呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.00,0:05:49.68,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,卡思嘉小姐 卡思嘉小姐沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.16,0:05:51.51,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事 能有什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.26,0:05:55.81,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,晚餐前因為肚子餓了就回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.34,0:06:01.23,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 這下能睡覺了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.85,0:06:08.15,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,淨找麻煩 保姆都迷路可怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.30,0:06:14.41,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,塞爾彼高
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.90,0:06:15.66,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.53,0:06:18.16,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,讓你費心了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.91,0:06:21.60,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.60,0:06:22.33,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.51,0:06:26.68,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,您要回去嗎 回聖都
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.63,0:06:33.76,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,誰會 誰會要回去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.51,0:06:43.04,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你們要去巴利達尼斯的話 最好小心些
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.28,0:06:47.98,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那裡現在是各國聯合軍的鎮守府
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.38,0:06:53.49,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多和庫夏人的大戰要一觸即發了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.57,0:07:01.00,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,聯合軍趕跑庫夏人後 他們也會肆意割占土地的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.12,0:07:06.34,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,米特蘭國說不定就被連根拔起了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.99,0:07:09.97,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不過和我們放羊的也沒什麼關係
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.29,0:07:13.84,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你是米特蘭人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.94,0:07:15.85,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那還真是太可憐了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.29,0:07:19.77,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我只是借了點人情而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.96,0:07:24.80,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 對了對了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.18,0:07:26.19,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,差點忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.81,0:07:29.48,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,走這條路的話要小心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.70,0:07:31.65,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,特別是山那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.06,0:07:33.20,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了 大爺
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.20,0:07:34.87,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,有山賊出沒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.82,0:07:37.87,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,要是山賊還算好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.36,0:07:40.83,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,出來是出來 但不是人類
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.04,0:07:42.43,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是獸鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.49,0:07:44.62,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,獸鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.66,0:07:53.22,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡 怎樣才能打到格斯一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.36,0:07:56.43,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,乾脆丟石頭怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.60,0:07:58.43,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不用劍就沒有意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.43,0:08:01.81,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,丟石頭你還是可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.26,0:08:04.13,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那當然
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.89,0:08:08.02,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,肉到手了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.27,0:08:12.03,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,雙手嗎 效果不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.62,0:08:34.72,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,混帳 果然不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.65,0:08:38.80,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不是那樣 你做得還不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.75,0:08:42.27,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但只招呼下三路敵人的眼睛就會適應
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.86,0:08:44.78,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你要下工夫不要讓敵人抓住你套路
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.16,0:08:49.81,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,最後一擊向著穿帷子的地方比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.27,0:08:52.86,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,因為你的腕力還不足以穿透鎧甲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.10,0:08:54.32,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.81,0:08:58.99,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.17,0:08:59.87,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.10,0:09:06.21,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,一般修行不是花費很長時間來重複練習基本功和傳授技巧嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.53,0:09:08.29,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是每天都在基礎訓練嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.70,0:09:09.63,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.86,0:09:14.92,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你打算修煉個幾十年 等成為高手再出陣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.29,0:09:16.88,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,真是夠漫長了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.08,0:09:18.47,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我可沒那樣打算
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.88,0:09:21.64,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼現在只能鍛鍊現有的技巧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.17,0:09:24.64,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你到至今為止 都是那麼做的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.01,0:09:28.31,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你真溫柔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.10,0:09:33.65,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,可以的話 能和我一起去撿柴火嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.33,0:09:50.08,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,都濕了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.74,0:09:53.09,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多就開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.45,0:09:54.55,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,開始什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.73,0:09:59.22,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,別裝傻了 想和我做個了斷才要兩人單獨出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.40,0:10:04.64,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,您說什麼呢 我只是想和格斯先生加深信任呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.81,0:10:06.64,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我是開玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.09,0:10:10.60,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,真無聊 你沒想法的話我就走了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.22,0:10:16.86,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我的玩笑是希望你去死
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.06,0:10:20.49,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,果然又擺起那時候的臉了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.76,0:10:24.27,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 這是法爾納塞小姐自身期望的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.36,0:10:28.37,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那副哭過後如同幼兒的神情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.89,0:10:31.25,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那樣無防備的她我毫無知曉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.74,0:10:34.61,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你改變了她
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.08,0:10:38.56,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,只要法爾納塞小姐繼續這個旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.56,0:10:42.59,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我就以侍從的身份和你好好合作
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.23,0:10:44.97,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你真是勞心費力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.64,0:10:48.60,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼 什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.06,0:10:49.64,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.84,0:10:52.48,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋 是山賊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.47,0:10:57.28,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,好 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.27,0:11:00.01,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙不是人類
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.01,0:11:00.70,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.82,0:11:06.58,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.20,0:11:09.83,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,獸鬼要出來了 不是人類
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.92,0:11:11.21,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這傢伙就是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.08,0:11:17.21,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.41,0:11:22.68,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,他會死吧 我們怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.23,0:11:36.90,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不怕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.14,0:11:39.68,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡的猩猩 滾開吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.95,0:11:51.87,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,伊斯多洛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.51,0:11:54.04,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,要被殺了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.16,0:12:00.09,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,樹果嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.63,0:12:04.55,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不要動
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.04,0:12:05.68,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,看看四周
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.55,0:12:09.72,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼時候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.67,0:12:11.98,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你們也到這邊來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.68,0:12:23.03,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,聽好了 無論發生什麼也不要離開或破壞這個圓陣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.32,0:12:24.65,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.77,0:12:27.28,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是魔法 魔法的儀式
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.40,0:12:28.37,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.70,0:12:30.24,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼說難道你是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.78,0:12:32.58,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 就是你想的那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.67,0:12:33.54,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是 魔 女 喲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.55,0:12:34.06,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.20,0:12:36.54,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是同伴 好懷念啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.16,0:12:39.09,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,尤多·海恩 班·海恩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.47,0:12:40.57,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,阿朵耐·佐巴特
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.06,0:12:42.13,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,艾·海恩·尤
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.73,0:12:43.72,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,阿格魯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.38,0:12:46.78,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,嗚啊 來了 來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.71,0:12:51.68,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.57,0:13:06.03,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.10,0:13:07.20,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,到底怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.73,0:13:11.12,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,恕我直言
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.64,0:13:14.50,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你們還是趕緊離開這裡為好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.99,0:13:17.00,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不用你擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.20,0:13:20.12,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我們已經習慣對付那種怪物了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.33,0:13:21.21,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,說句實話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.21,0:13:24.05,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,以你用劍的水準下次就死定了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.18,0:13:25.07,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.07,0:13:26.72,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你給我等等老太婆
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.48,0:13:32.68,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這個是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.47,0:13:35.02,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不是老太婆的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.63,0:13:37.27,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不如說基本上就沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.35,0:13:41.44,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.39,0:13:46.29,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.30,0:13:47.70,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,法爾納塞小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.06,0:13:49.11,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,發生什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.36,0:13:50.17,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.17,0:13:50.96,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這個人沒救了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.02,0:13:56.66,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事 那兩個人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.03,0:14:01.00,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,就好像扭曲是由那兩人引起的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.74,0:14:03.84,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡啾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.68,0:14:06.88,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那個魔女小鬼啾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.26,0:14:08.80,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,對於你來說已經做得很好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.25,0:14:10.30,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.64,0:14:13.39,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你向我道謝反而背後一冷啾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.26,0:14:18.23,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,反正結果也是被那個魔女救的你這個小猴子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.01,0:14:24.15,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,已經不想再發生那種事了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.32,0:14:30.41,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,已經完全黏上法爾納塞小姐了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.53,0:14:32.62,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是 是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.90,0:14:39.28,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不要玩了 喂 我說
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.36,0:14:42.28,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,住手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.28,0:14:43.67,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,趕緊住手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.32,0:14:49.05,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.00,0:14:50.97,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.84,0:14:54.64,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,到底發生什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.00,0:14:56.97,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,被獸鬼襲擊了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.61,0:15:00.60,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,本來有五個伙伴的 但是全部
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.04,0:15:03.77,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我也不能就這麼回村裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.76,0:15:07.69,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我有不得不去的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.23,0:15:11.49,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我是住在依羅克村的摩根
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.04,0:15:14.57,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你們旅人可能不太清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.32,0:15:19.62,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這附近以前就有很多妖精和魔女的傳言
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.20,0:15:25.54,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,雖這麼說但是打從心底相信的人沒多少
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.46,0:15:29.26,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,直到那個可怕的夜晚來到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.75,0:15:31.09,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,可怕的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.46,0:15:34.51,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,一群獸鬼襲擊了村子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.29,0:15:38.85,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,就像從故事跑出來的一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.88,0:15:42.31,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,他們盡情大鬧了一場
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.89,0:15:46.65,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,從那天起世界就改變了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.18,0:15:50.90,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,就好像之前的日子都是假的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.34,0:15:54.11,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你可直接告訴領主啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.26,0:15:57.83,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,領主已經出兵去了布利達尼斯了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.01,0:15:59.83,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,現在城堡就是空城
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.41,0:16:02.16,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,就算見到領主
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.57,0:16:07.09,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,他們會為了獸鬼這種迷信出兵嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.60,0:16:09.21,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那你們打算怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.85,0:16:11.67,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,用傳說對付傳說
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.61,0:16:13.51,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.08,0:16:17.41,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我們想向魔女求救
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.87,0:16:18.43,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.42,0:16:24.27,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這座森林深處傳說有魔女的洋館
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.68,0:16:30.53,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那裡是只有館主人招來的人才能到達
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.10,0:16:34.32,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,意思是這座森林被魔女施了魔法對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.44,0:16:38.91,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼不管怎麼找都找不到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.65,0:16:44.41,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,之前三不五時就有見過的小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.96,0:16:49.46,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,有人穿過結界了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.24,0:16:52.17,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,元素靈們
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.17,0:16:55.97,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.61,0:16:58.57,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這個是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.44,0:17:16.82,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那個果然不是夢境
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.98,0:17:19.87,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然沒有人相信
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.30,0:17:25.12,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,時過境遷我都把它當成夢境了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.24,0:17:30.41,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那個魔女小鬼也在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.70,0:17:33.84,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼 這種奇妙的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.12,0:17:36.63,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,伊斯多洛 離開那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.17,0:17:40.43,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.61,0:17:42.72,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這個一臉蠢樣的石像
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.80,0:17:46.98,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼啊 真好笑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.98,0:18:03.87,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,請等等 好好交談一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.98,0:18:05.08,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,摩根大爺
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.36,0:18:07.08,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不是能對話的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.20,0:18:08.50,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,老爺子趕緊躲起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.96,0:18:17.97,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,長出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.71,0:18:21.43,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,死靈 還是使徒的手段
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.26,0:18:30.30,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這可是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.70,0:18:35.27,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,呀 好噁心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.44,0:18:40.90,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事啊 這些傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.20,0:18:48.70,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,沒完沒了啊這個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.88,0:18:55.45,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我說 我說挺厲害的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.45,0:18:56.88,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那個男人的劍
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.08,0:19:06.06,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那個是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.22,0:19:12.94,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,大家聽我說 人偶胸口記號附近藏著小人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.94,0:19:15.82,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,把那個掏出來 人偶就不會再生了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.47,0:19:17.73,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,哎啊 暴露了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.18,0:19:20.44,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此 這下明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.86,0:19:24.09,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,伊斯多洛飛踢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.32,0:19:25.99,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.28,0:19:30.35,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦啊 史爾基 全都要打壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.77,0:19:32.16,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.24,0:19:33.75,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,停手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.50,0:19:39.95,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.04,0:19:41.63,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,突然停下了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.38,0:19:51.27,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 果然是那時的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.88,0:19:52.98,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.64,0:19:55.47,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,大家請移步屋裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.60,0:19:57.65,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,師傅想要見你們
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.82,0:19:59.65,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,喔 求之不得
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.18,0:20:02.18,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,一決勝負吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.23,0:20:03.49,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.49,0:20:07.45,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,好不容易的邀請 就去見識一下魔女吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.55,0:20:11.41,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼好有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.41,0:20:14.87,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,說是屋子更像是巢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.26,0:20:17.08,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺變成松鼠了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.09,0:20:17.75,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那邊的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.17,0:20:20.46,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,不要擅自玩桌子上的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.78,0:20:21.46,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.14,0:20:24.93,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,話說魔女不是你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.25,0:20:28.13,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我是史爾基還在修行中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.13,0:20:30.93,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我是依巴蕾拉 是這孩子的隨從
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.42,0:20:33.73,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼啊 半桶水的菜鳥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.18,0:20:37.31,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我是伊斯多洛 那時真是承蒙照顧了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.34,0:20:40.15,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,託你的福 返祖了整整半天
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.27,0:20:43.24,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因為你抱住了奇怪的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.48,0:20:46.26,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪的地方 不好好說出來不明白啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.26,0:20:47.57,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是猴子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.77,0:20:49.73,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,所以說就是奇怪的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.07,0:20:51.08,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是歐派
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.15,0:20:52.16,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.26,0:20:54.37,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,所以說歐派
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.37,0:20:55.24,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.25,0:20:57.29,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,住手吧 好煩人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.74,0:21:00.50,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你還是快點引薦我們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.20,0:21:02.72,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,去見你師傅
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.08,0:21:04.22,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,請這邊走
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.25,0:21:06.34,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我把客人帶來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.44,0:21:07.18,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,師傅
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.38,0:21:14.14,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,歡迎來到靈樹之館
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.97,0:21:17.27,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,請原諒弟子的無禮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.36,0:21:19.73,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,她只是為了保護我的安全
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.44,0:21:21.73,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.23,0:21:24.07,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我還以為是尖鼻子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.08,0:21:27.07,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,滿臉皺紋的老妖怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.08,0:21:28.45,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,無禮之人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.36,0:21:33.16,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你 我就當是讚美收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.28,0:21:37.00,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,五十年前的那天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.00,0:21:39.00,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我用從您那得到的藥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.00,0:21:42.21,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,把我母親從生死邊緣救回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.66,0:21:43.88,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,無法相信
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.50,0:21:46.72,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,是當時的模樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.38,0:21:50.80,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我還記得你就是那時的小孩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.14,0:21:52.39,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,好懷念啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.42,0:21:58.60,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,在你剝奪生命的人當中沒有我的同胞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.00,0:22:04.03,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,就算有也是你們侍奉神明的人全體的錯誤
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.32,0:22:07.90,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒有向你一人報復的打算
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.44,0:22:09.57,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.48,0:22:12.48,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,還有烙印的兩位
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.28,0:22:14.29,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎麼知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.28,0:22:17.33,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,真高興能見面
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.76,0:22:20.98,DefaultSub,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直等著與你們相見
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.20,0:03:20.11,DefaultUp,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.92,0:03:23.12,DefaultUp,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.52,0:21:01.94,DefaultUp,NTP,0,0,0,,你們智障啊
Comment: 0,0:22:42.75,0:22:44.75,EDCht,,0,0,0,,/--------ED---------/
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.75,0:22:49.20,EDCht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}緋紅序幕  緩緩拉開
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.20,0:22:53.15,EDCht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}笑談之間  揭開舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.15,0:22:57.08,EDCht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}台上一切  皆為戲劇
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.08,0:23:00.50,EDCht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}循序漸進  如詩如畫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.50,0:23:10.09,EDCht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}一字之差  終局俱變
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.09,0:23:18.57,EDCht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}索然無味  其為傳說
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.15,0:23:23.89,EDCht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}利慾之心  隱於夜中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.89,0:23:27.96,EDCht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}日升之前  一觸即發
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.96,0:23:32.63,EDCht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}純真羽翼  散落人間
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.63,0:23:37.33,EDCht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}應著之色  是黑是白
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.33,0:23:39.41,EDCht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}不得而知  好奇尚異
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.41,0:23:43.29,EDCht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}餘音裊裊  不絕於耳
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.29,0:23:47.21,EDCht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}何人願聞  何人可應
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.21,0:23:52.36,EDCht,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}虛浮年華  何需再度
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.75,0:22:49.20,EDJap,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}鮮明な赤の緞帳を引く
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.20,0:22:53.15,EDJap,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}歓声の中  舞台へ上がる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.15,0:22:57.08,EDJap,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}全て予定調和の戯曲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.08,0:23:00.50,EDJap,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}狂いは無い  絵画の様に
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.50,0:23:10.09,EDJap,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}たった一字が欠けた時に結末は変わる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.09,0:23:18.57,EDJap,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}呆気無い程に  それが 物語
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.15,0:23:23.89,EDJap,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}夜に隠したambition  greed
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.89,0:23:27.96,EDJap,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}朝が来る前に放て
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.96,0:23:32.63,EDJap,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}無邪気に散り降る羽
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.63,0:23:37.33,EDJap,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}染まるべき色は白か黒か
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.33,0:23:39.41,EDJap,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}知らない  知りたい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.41,0:23:43.29,EDJap,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}木霊するostinato
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.29,0:23:47.21,EDJap,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}誰か聴いて  誰か応えて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.21,0:23:52.36,EDJap,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,150)}仮初の日々はもう要らない
Comment: 0,0:01:41.55,0:01:43.55,OPCht,,0,0,0,,/--------OP---------/
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.55,0:01:51.37,OPCht,,0,0,0,,刻下的烙印如何磨滅
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.87,0:02:00.83,OPCht,,0,0,0,,任憑他人道長短  殊死之斗又何曾徒勞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.86,0:02:11.17,OPCht,,0,0,0,,暗啞了的嘶吼  依舊在耳畔激盪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.74,0:02:17.42,OPCht,,0,0,0,,笑至盡頭之人不是我  亦無怨無悔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.42,0:02:21.33,OPCht,,0,0,0,,唯願能夠守護你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.60,0:02:26.97,OPCht,,0,0,0,,誅盡來敵戰至終
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.97,0:02:29.66,OPCht,,0,0,0,,逆天而行破宿命
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.66,0:02:34.60,OPCht,,0,0,0,,思思纏繞神之手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.60,0:02:39.12,OPCht,,0,0,0,,欲斷枷鎖魂難斷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.47,0:02:44.90,OPCht,,0,0,0,,若能終結一切以戰止戈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.90,0:02:48.41,OPCht,,0,0,0,,焚盡我身又何妨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.91,0:02:56.78,OPCht,,0,0,0,,困獸猶鬥  逆境之中尋生存
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.55,0:01:51.37,OPJap,,0,0,0,,\h\h\h\h\h\h\h刻まれた烙印は  最早消せはしないと
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.87,0:02:00.83,OPJap,,0,0,0,,足掻くだけ時間の無駄だと  誰が言おうと
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.86,0:02:11.17,OPJap,,0,0,0,,また聞こえてくる叫び  声にもならない声で
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.74,0:02:17.42,OPJap,,0,0,0,,最後に笑うのはおれじゃなくていい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.42,0:02:21.33,OPJap,,0,0,0,,そこにおまえがいれば
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.60,0:02:26.97,OPJap,,0,0,0,,戦いの果てまで辿り着くため
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.97,0:02:29.66,OPJap,,0,0,0,,運命(さだめ)を越えて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.66,0:02:34.60,OPJap,,0,0,0,,断ち切れない  神の手でも
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.60,0:02:39.12,OPJap,,0,0,0,,結んだ絆と魂を
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.47,0:02:44.90,OPJap,,0,0,0,,戦いの果てまで辿り着くため
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.90,0:02:48.41,OPJap,,0,0,0,,すべてを懸けて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.91,0:02:56.78,OPJap,,0,0,0,,足掻き続けて　生き抜いてみせるだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.00,0:24:07.09,Preview,,0,0,0,,{\an7}你們怎麼知道烙印的事
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.05,0:24:11.13,Preview,,0,0,0,,他依然還活著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.26,0:24:15.43,Preview,,0,0,0,,{\an9}那是 活祭品的烙印
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.51,0:24:19.60,Preview,,0,0,0,,{\an9}史爾基 去助他們一臂之力
